 />\n報導中稱，在確定費sir病情後，醫生會通過手術進行治療。手術後的康復過程會非常緩慢，一般術後患者會面臨疲勞、頭痛以及睡眠問題等症狀。<br />\n<br />\n這樣疾病症狀對於費格遜這樣一個77歲的老人來說無疑是非常嚴重的，根據在美國心臟聯合會發表的論文《蛛網膜下腔出血的危險因素：系統回顧》，這種疾病的死亡率高達50%。但在接受治療後，死亡率則會有所下降，但在接受治療後的患者中，只有不到五分之一的患者不會受到後遺症的困擾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cb3e82876a66a2312bff6cfe750ba626c0e758","tid":654611,"uid":55,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab298a6c21df878222f16cd11833d50b4853e547","tid":654611,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ee325b086646b96dbe23170b17e3a1715ad87fa","tid":654611,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a045e8d46a76f48ec99bec840e9b4d5bda3a49","tid":654611,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1c888d63904cd4a68821516dbf55a1101b4594dd","tid":654611,"uid":18867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3048a14976cdd4f3b5fbffdb76e7bc326ac8c834","tid":654611,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8542a99ae0612d3ef0fb12eb851b02ea322c88a3","tid":654611,"uid":67252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"雲加...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T19:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/44b26d1fd706368ed30d4e541647544f/tumblr_p80dm8ZLJ31tmoqudo1_540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F44b26d1fd706368ed30d4e541647544f%2Ftumblr_p80dm8ZLJ31tmoqudo1_540.jpg&h=235a3fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img sr